      "text": "doesn't know what they are.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "\"It is our purpose in organizing ICARF to find the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "answer to the UFO mystery, and give the facts to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "the public. And in order to do this we will need",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "the assistance of every person concerned. Persons",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "with movie and still cameras are particularly needed,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "the emphasis is on photographic data, despite",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "the fact that sightings with binoculars and telescopes,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "sound detector and ham radio stations are also very",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "important in the process of our research.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "\"All persons interested in setting up observer posts",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "who can devote from one to three hours a day on skywatch,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "and who can be relied upon to have their cameras loaded",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "and ready to photograph these objects should immediately",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "contact us for full information. Adult Skywatch clubs,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "high school groups, science clubs, industrial groups and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "individuals in general are all particularly asked to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "join us in our search for the answer to the UFOs.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "\"Contact us at the address above.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "INTER CONTINENTAL AERIAL",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "RESEARCH FOUNDATION\"",
